data.description:
This exquisite brick colonial offers an abundance of space and top-notch features, making it the perfect haven for your family. With 4 bedrooms, 2.5
bathrooms, and a 3-car garage, this home combines elegance with practicality.Indulge in the serene retreat of the master suite, complete with a jet
tub and a walk-in shower, providing a spa-like experience right at home. This residence boasts a brand new roof, dual pane windows, and a recently
installed AC unit (2021), ensuring comfort and energy efficiency year-round. An added filter system caters to those with allergies.The living room is
equipped with a surround sound system and cameo lights, creating an inviting space for gatherings and relaxation. A first-floor laundry adds
convenience to your daily routines.The massive finished basement with tall ceilings offers a versatile space for a playroom, home gym, or
entertainment area, providing endless possibilities for customization. All bedrooms, including the master, feature vaulted ceilings, adding a touch of
grandeur to each space. A private fenced-in yard provides a safe and intimate outdoor space for play and relaxation. A large and convenient
driveway leads to a 3-car garage, providing ample parking and storage options. The expansive yard offers plenty of room for outdoor activities and
potential landscaping projects.This home provides a comfortable living environment for your family. Don't miss the opportunity to make this
exceptional property your forever home!
